Package com.simplegeo.client.handler

Interface Summary
SimpleGeoResponseHandler A handler designed to be called using a JSON string received as part of an HTTP Response.
 

Class Summary
GeoJSONHandler A response handler used for creating Features and FeatureCollections.
GeoJSONRecordHandler A response handler used for creating Records from a given payload.
JSONHandler A response handler that converts the payload into a JSONObject.
JSONLayerHandler A response handler used for creating Layers from a given payload.
ListHandler A response handler used for creating CategoryCollection from a given payload
